== Aẓur n yism ==
Awal Tasenselkimt iga yan wawal nna ɣ llan sin iwaliwn ad tnt igan : '''ssn''' i d-ikkan tussna, d '''slkim''' i d-ikkan aslkm nɣ ar islkam inɣmissn.

== Amzruy ==
Iga Charles Babbage yan wajinyuṛ igan u tmazirt n Ingliz, nttan ad isnulfan ɣ usggwas n 1822 tikti n umutur n umgird, i usiḍn n yigtfuln n tusnakt. Ɣ usggwas n 1834, isuffɣ-d tikti n umutur usliḍ lli iṭṭafn akk tulmisin n uslkim. Amma aslkim atrar, Alan Turing, yan umusnak zɣ tmazirt n Ingliz ula ntta, i d-isrsn imnzayn nns ɣ 1936. Ma d nttini Tamacint n Turing. Nzḍar ad nini Turing d ababat n tsenselkimt.
